title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Description: Exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When trying to export data from a table that contains a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row, an exception is thrown.
SR:
To reproduce the bug:

1. Add a table with a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.
2. Preview the attached report.
3. Attempt to export the data.
